::DevilDuer::

DevilDuer nods. "Yup, way up there," he says about the rank question, then 
going on to answer Diamond's other questions, "I'm takin' ya to the lab. 
We'll get you checked out and see the extent of the damage."

He walks into the lab, placing her on a table. "Now jus' lean back and we'll 
get ya taken care of."
